title: Insan
subTitle: Ajit Rathod, a grieving policeman, vows to catch his wife's killer, terrorist Azhar Khan. He pursues Azhar with single-minded focus, overcoming all hurdles.

title: Chingaari
subTitle: A novice postmaster in Rangpur unexpectedly becomes entangled in the complex lives of local sex workers, challenging his preconceptions.

title: Jagan
subTitle: Jagan, an artist by profession, befriends two siblings on separate occasions and they both fall in love with him. He is forcibly married to the elder sister by goons, creating troubles in his life.

title: Baat Bann Gayi
subTitle: Kabir falls in love with Rachna, but he must impress her brother, Professor Laxmi Nivas, to get her hand in marriage. Things turn upside down when his lookalike shows up.

title: Aasman Se Ooncha
subTitle: Inspector Malik transfers to Mumbai along with his family and sets out on a mission to catch King, an underworld leader. However, a shocking revelation changes the course of their lives.

title: Kaali Topi Laal Rumaal
subTitle: Commando Vijay arrests a terrorist, Master DD. However, he realises that Master DD is just a pawn and tries to find the real culprit.

title: Vaishnavi
subTitle: Born with the divine power, Vaishnavi receives treatment as a goddess by the villagers. After getting killed, she possesses the body of another girl who looks like her to exact revenge for her death.

title: Andhaa Kaanoon
subTitle: Two siblings, Vijay and Durga, vow to avenge the death of their parents. So, Durga becomes an inspector to punish the criminals, whereas Vijay breaks the law to achieve his goal.

title: Baazigar
subTitle: A cold-blooded killer with a vendetta charms a businessman's elder daughter and then kills her in a way that would make it seem like a case of suicide. He then plots to destroy the rest of the family.

title: Dhadkan
subTitle: Anjali and Dev's love story faces a harsh twist when Anjali is forced to marry Ram. Years later, Dev returns to rekindle their romance, only to find that Anjali has grown to love her husband.

title: Mera Faisla
subTitle: Raj wishes to marry Rati but faces humiliation from her father due to the stigma associated with his lineage. Soon, he decides to join the police force to restore his family's honour.

title: Udhaar
subTitle: A young woman becomes anxious for her life when she discovers that there is a dangerous murderer out on the loose.

title: Krishna Arjun
subTitle: After hearing the news of his mother's death, a man travels home to find his brother has been arrested for rape and murder. He sets out to uncover the truth.

title: International Crook
subTitle: Rajesh, the superintendent of the police, is happy to meet his old friend, Shekar, in Goa, unaware that he is a smuggler, who is involved in a spree of illegal activities.

title: Rustum
subTitle: Abhishek Bhargav, a police officer, decides to avenge the death of his friend, DCP Bharath. When his investigation lands him in Bengaluru, he discovers the roots of an organ trading mafia.

title: Sher Ka Shikaar
subTitle: A man, who is famous in his village for killing man-eating tigers, unwillingly becomes a part of a conspiracy surrounding illegal drugs.

title: Keemat: They Are Back
subTitle: Two crooks accidentally kill a man and decide to inform his parents about the bad news. However, once they meet the family, they end up lying to them.

title: Teri Meherbaniyan
subTitle: Ram, an honest man, falls in love with a woman named Bijli and goes on to help the people of her village. However, the region's corrupt leader, Thakur Vijay Singh, soon begins to plot against him.

title: The Real Tiger
subTitle: When a truck collides with his car, an exemplary politician goes into a coma. His police officer son learns that the accident is a deliberate attack and sets out to hunt down the perpetrators and exact his revenge.

title: The Real Tiger
subTitle: When a truck collides with his car, an exemplary politician goes into a coma. His police officer son learns that the accident is a deliberate attack and sets out to hunt down the perpetrators and exact his revenge.

title: Star
subTitle: Dev belongs to a middle class family and dreams of becoming a music sensation like his icon Elvis Presley. However, his reality forces him to give up on his dream until he finds a job at Charlie's disco.

title: Khatarnak Khel
subTitle: A young girl loses her parents in an accident due to illegal bike racers in Chennai. She soon sets out to exact revenge on the racer responsible for her parents' death.

title: Kundan
subTitle: Thakur Shamsher Singh, a wealthy criminal, tries to befriend a newly-appointed police officer in order to gain his favour, only to find out that the policeman is immune to his tactics.

title: Antim Nyay
subTitle: Jay Singh encounters Seema while struggling to seek justice for his deceased father. As the couple attempts to live a happy life, unforeseen circumstances invite more troubles.

title: Jaan Se Pyaara
subTitle: Inspector Jai balances working as a cop with taking care of his mother and a brother with developmental disabilities. But when he arrests a local don, he starts to fear for his family's safety.

title: Juaari
subTitle: The struggle against a dangerous gambling lord tests Dharam Singh and Vijay as they navigate crime, deception and violence to protect the innocent and reclaim what was lost.

title: Mela
subTitle: Best mates Kishen and Shankar decide to help village belle Roopa avenge her family's death, but their friendship is tested in the process.

title: Phool Aur Kaante
subTitle: Love leads Ajay down a new path when he is expected to inherit his father's criminal empire, bringing along perils that could either tear their family apart or solidify their bond.

title: Aashiq
subTitle: Pooja and Chander fall in love and want to be together. However, since Pooja's alcoholic father would never approve, she decides to run away from her house but, unfortunately, lands in a brothel.
